Very short compilation tutorial
-------------------------------

1. Requirements

CMake (at least 2.8)
OpenCV (at least 2.4.3)
Boost (at least 1.48)

2. Compilation

a. create the compilation directory. Anything is okay as long as it is not
   located in source directory

b. enter compilation directory. run:
   cmake <opencv_descriptors_directory>

c. compile
   make

d. copy binary
   cp bin/opencv_descriptors <mvprmatlab_binaries_directory>

e. done
